{"tid":489154,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[處境題] 如果你係個新上任嘅領隊 你會點處置隊中深得民心但冇球技嘅隊長?","createTime":"2017-12-04T11:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T13:25:22.000Z","uid":132961,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4712f2ed680276d7fa210a39984507091e86251a","tid":489154,"uid":132961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:36:48.000Z","msg":"假設你新官上任<br />\n第一個工作就係處理隊長嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n個隊長深得隊友尊重<br />\n而且地位原因 之前一直都係必然主力<br />\n每個領隊都唔敢放佢落後備<br />\n<br />\n但係因為年紀大<br />\n打正選會拖累隊波<br />\n有佢在內嘅比賽<br />\n球隊又慢又冇活力 成日輸<br />\n<br />\n但一上任就掃走佢<br />\n一定會影響到士氣<br />\n甚至令個領隊不受歡迎<br />\n更加難搞<br />\n<br />\n如果係你<br />\n你會為左民心而繼續逼住用佢<br />\n定係為左戰績 大刀闊斧掃走佢？"},{"pid":"0c66c7e0751aa4739a037378dfa7e7f36ce9a681","tid":489154,"uid":435,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:44:47.000Z","msg":"掃走佢 有成績就冇人反你"},{"pid":"a49d61ba16675f38f43e202fea68cde5b1122252","tid":489154,"uid":20736,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:46:52.000Z","msg":"同下佢傾計<br />\n叫佢自己交棒比下一個做隊長<br />\n廢事由我黎除佢章 咁就唔好睇<br />\n醒目嘅應該自己識退位讓賢<br />\n唔醒目就唯有比佢打多幾場然後除佢章"},{"pid":"dbdbeb843feb721cc1dfb0b4fb5192bcd5da9999","tid":489154,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:48:23.000Z","msg":"處理得唔好隨時好似AVB咁<br />\n林伯特M腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7702eff2e897c7740d9f92909c0e8bdb77fb9b10","tid":489154,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:48:43.000Z","msg":"開頭幾場比佢踢足 之後慢慢收緊佢上陣時間 比佢踢70分鐘 之後變到得60分鐘 再慢慢搵個人取締佢正選位囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c785a36fa157e97c3a8a74cab6d34a42a02922b9","tid":489154,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00a65b31163f295084e4563c3b1ab731e681f096","tid":489154,"uid":42246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>處理得唔好隨時好似AVB咁<br />\n林伯特M腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪屈啦 係你班主仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dad2256a8145fed3357248445409b8b3bba94e5c","tid":489154,"uid":42246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>處理得唔好隨時好似AVB咁<br />\n林伯特M腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪屈啦 係你班主仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2a32a953230007924592b4612ebe868f2aca62","tid":489154,"uid":10287,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T13:11:47.000Z","msg":"叫球員整傷左佢咪得囉"},{"pid":"e37245561a7ec67395357aed0e1a38d59fb29e1b","tid":489154,"uid":132961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:27:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>處理得唔好隨時好似AVB咁<br />\n林伯特M腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\navb唔係處理得唔好 直頭處理得差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇記錯係咪好似話連更衣室locker同停車場都唔俾班老將用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2cff7a2738f1c26528515daa4c63e49820a0557","tid":489154,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T18:48:05.000Z","msg":"個隊長係咪盧保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ec50dc