score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一睇以為講緊神軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n深得民心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"919a9c1e76c96e6fcbd2b5375bbbaf4935343f16","tid":489154,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T01:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一睇以為講緊神軒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n深得民心？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係冇球技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d488eabd7e5a208df765903d42842b3ddc2c9d97","tid":489154,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T02:01:15.000Z","msg":"上季車仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"018d3d5b6fc0faba93c93194e566d1719b3fa318","tid":489154,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"謝4 朗尼  呢堆<br />\n<br />\n曼同利 個做法<br />\n<br />\n都係等到差唔多完約"},{"pid":"27bc3225e88a49c478275fb3980db432831d3853","tid":489154,"uid":28353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"達海猛"},{"pid":"3a02bbd0d3514197f37e3748330386e47013b1e7","tid":489154,"uid":46933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"加佢入教練組<br />\n踢少d波都叫有貢獻"},{"pid":"9b91f9a1725cd0399bd2bbd4180f6d7bac7a3e2d","tid":489154,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:37:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>謝4 朗尼  呢堆<br />\n<br />\n曼同利 個做法<br />\n<br />\n都係等到差唔多完約</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 開始慢慢減少出場時間<br />\n2. 對續約冷處理 差唔多最後1，2年<br />\n3. 開教練組約 (去到呢步 好多球員都會自己走 一係撈金/一係去其他球會踢)<br />\n<br />\n真係好像上面好多人咁強硬處理 比例反而小<br />\n<br />\n曼 利 車 都係咁處理"}]}